Version: 1.1 · Last updated: 2026-05-14 · See "Document Review & Corrections" at end.

Project Overview

Brand Name

AirportFaster

Domain

airportfaster.com

Brand Positioning

AirportFaster is positioned as:

A Global Premium Airport Experience Platform.

The platform is not positioned as:

* A tourism office
* A transfer company
* A traditional travel agency
* A simple fast track booking website

Instead, AirportFaster is designed to become:

* A premium airport services marketplace
* A travel infrastructure platform
* A technology-enabled airport concierge ecosystem

⸻

Vision

Long-Term Vision

To become the leading global platform for premium airport services by aggregating airport assistance providers, lounges, concierge services, and airport-related premium experiences into a single unified ecosystem.

⸻

Initial Strategic Direction

Business Model Strategy

AirportFaster will initially operate as:

Marketplace + Human-Assisted Operations

Meaning:

* Suppliers provide the services
* AirportFaster owns the customer experience
* AirportFaster manages operations and support
* AirportFaster handles booking orchestration
* AirportFaster standardizes quality and communication

AirportFaster will NOT initially:

* Operate airport staff directly
* Employ airport agents in every airport
* Build physical infrastructure

