Airport Management Strategy

Centralized Airport Control

AirportFaster must provide a fully centralized airport management system controlled by the admin dashboard.

The admin team must have complete operational control over:

* Adding new airports
* Editing airport information
* Activating/deactivating airports
* Managing airport services
* Managing airport SEO pages
* Assigning suppliers per airport
* Configuring airport pricing
* Configuring supported services per airport
* Managing airport visibility on the public website

⸻

Dynamic Airport Publishing

When a new airport is added from the admin dashboard:

* The airport must automatically appear on the website
* Airport landing pages must auto-generate dynamically
* Airport services must instantly become searchable
* SEO metadata must be configurable
* Multi-language content must be manageable

The platform architecture must support scalable airport expansion without requiring developer intervention for every new airport.

